Detailed Description

cvmx_fpa_que8_page_index

FPA_QUE8_PAGE_INDEX = FPA's Queue7 Page Index

The present index page for queue 7 of the FPA. This number reflects the number of pages of pointers that have been written to memory for this queue. Because the address space is 38-bits the number of 128 byte pages could cause this register value to wrap.
